AUDIO: 'You can\'t hide because what I built today can track human movement in real time from kilometers away without Wi-Fi, without internet, and without a camera. Sounds impossible? Well, let me prove'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it. This is the live radar interface, and that dot right there, that\'s my brother. As he moves, you can see the position updating in real time. And the craziest part, this data is coming from'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
